{"service_name": "Methods Advisory: Governance and Assurance Services", "service_id": "4712658955665408", "company_name": "Methods Advisory Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Methods Advisory Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Methods Advisory: Governance and Assurance Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Methods Advisory assists at all stages of the CCS \u201cGateway\u201d or equivalent process, from initial review process through to post- implementation reviews. This includes assessment on the likelihood of delivery, risks or issues facing the project and an independent external challenge on the robustness and sustainability of investment plans/ processes\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Underpinned by recognised methodologies, e.g. MSP and Prince2\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Emphasis on Stakeholder engagement within governance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Incorporates robust use of business investment cases\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can be applied at different levels of management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focuses on pragmatic application, not slavish methodologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Applies a managed, proportionate risk-based approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Takes a benefits/ value- led approach to reviews\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Complies with CCS Gateway/ equivalent scrutiny/ assurance approaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accommodates the whole life cycle of change and BAU\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Uses experienced and qualified staff, including CCS Gateway Reviewers\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Low/ no learning curve, with staff who understand your business\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better knowledge transfer through proven tools and processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Governance that is evidence and benefits-led\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better, more effective stakeholder engagement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Emphasis on tracking measurable quality and outcome improvements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Able to draw on relevant experience across all public services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More resilience to external scrutiny through \u2018safe\u2019 independent challenge\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More pragmatic, proportionate, managed approach to risks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stronger engagement through user and citizen involvement\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3300 to \u00a31750 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92308/4712658955665408-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92308/4712658955665408-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92308/4712658955665408-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92308/4712658955665408-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4712\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6589\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5566\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5408\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Methods Advisory Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Bid Team\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n      